Author: lazyrainy
Text: Smaaaaart!! I’m anticipating not takin my full breaks so that’s a good tip! Thanks :)

Author: sadbeech210
Text: I'm a nurse! I always make sure to pack my lunch so I'm not tempted by the amount of food that's always around (maybe that's just the place I work idk if all nurses stations look like a convenience store snack isle). I also make sure to bring high protein snacks that are fast so I dont have to actually sit down and eat them (Premier protein shakes, light mozzarella cheese, greek yogurt, those sort of things). Also lots of coffee.
